description.narrative: This activity (SNP: Procurement of Solar Equipment) is a component of Solar Nigeria Programme reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £52,087,915. This component benefits Nigeria, and works in the following sector(s): Public sector policy and administrative management, Energy generation, renewable sources - multiple technologies, Environmental policy and administrative management. , with the following implementing partners: Adam Smith International, AECOM, Crown Agents Limited. The start date is 01-10-2014 and the end date is 30-11-2021.
